## How we work

Every iGaming engagement starts with understanding your market position, licensed jurisdictions, and competitive landscape.

1. **Audit and analysis.** I review your technical infrastructure, content quality, backlink profile, and competitor positioning. This gives us a clear baseline and identifies the highest-impact opportunities.
2. **Strategy development.** Based on the audit, I build a prioritised roadmap covering technical fixes, content gaps, authority building, and compliance alignment. Everything maps back to revenue — more qualified traffic, more sign-ups, more deposits.
3. **Execution support.** I work alongside your development and content teams to implement changes. For clients without in-house resource, I can manage execution through my network of specialist iGaming writers and developers.
4. **Ongoing optimisation.** iGaming SEO is not a one-off project. Odds content needs constant freshness. Competitors are always moving. I provide ongoing [SEO consulting](/services/seo-consulting) to keep your strategy ahead of algorithm updates, competitor moves, and regulatory changes.

## Pricing

iGaming SEO consulting starts from £2,500 per month for ongoing retainers, reflecting the specialist knowledge, competitive intensity, and compliance requirements of the vertical.

For one-off audits or strategy projects, pricing depends on the scope — number of markets, site size, and technical complexity. [Contact me](/contact) with details about your operation and I will provide a clear proposal within 48 hours.

